ACADEMIC ATTRIBUTIONS

The SURD (Signed-Unique-Redundant Decomposition) algorithm is based on:

"Quantifying high-order synergistic and redundant information decomposition
in neural spiking data"
Authors: Pica, G., Piasini, E., Chicharro, D., & Panzeri, S.
Published in: Nature Communications, vol. 15, Article number: 8553 (2024)
DOI: https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-024-53373-4
License: Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)

Reference implementation: https://github.com/panzerilab/SURD

================================================================================

The SCIC (Signed Causal Information Components) algorithm is an original
contribution by Andrey Kolkov, developed using AI-powered development tools.

